---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
import PROFESSIONAL from "../components/Professional.astro"
---

<Layout title="Velavan Medical | About Us">
    <div class = "pt-4 pl-4 pr-4">
    <div class="widget-imgcontainer" >
         <h2 class = "pt-6 font-bold sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">About Us</h2>
                <p class= "pt-5 pb-3 font-semibold">At Velavan Medicals, we are dedicated to providing the highest quality healthcare <br>products and services. </p>
    </div>
    </div>

<!-- Section 1 -->
<section class="pb-16 md:pt-28 md:pb-24 overflow-hidden relative">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5 parallax" data-speed="0.2">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-repeat" style="background-image: url('/dot-pattern.png');"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="container-custom relative">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="animate-on-scroll delay-4">
        <div class="relative hover-zoom rounded-xl">
          <div class="absolute -inset-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple to-blue rounded-xl blur opacity-30 transition-opacity duration-300 hover:opacity-50"></div>
          <div class="relative bg-white rounded-xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
            <img 
              src="/counter-section.jpg" 
              alt="Velavan Medical banner" 
              class="w-full h-auto transition-all duration-500"
              width="700"
              height="500"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
        <div class="pl-10">
                <div class="pt-10">
                <h1 class="animate-on-scroll delay-0 text-blue text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold leading-tight">
                   Legacy of Excellence
                </h1>    
            </div>        
                <p class="animate-on-scroll delay-1 mt-6 text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-lg">
                    Founded in 1961 by the visionary duo K. A. Abdul Hai and     K.A. Sheik Dawood, Bawa Medical Mart has been
                    a cornerstone of trust and excellence in the medical supplies industry for over 63 years. With a legacy built
                    on reliability and dedication, we are proud to serve generations of customers with high-quality medical products and solutions.
                    We are more than just a supplier we are a partner in your journey toward better health.
                    From home delivery services to personalized support, our mission is to simplify healthcare for our community. With a blend of 
                    traditional values and modern innovations, Bawa Medical Mart continues to lead as a trusted name in medical care. 
                </p> 
        </div>       
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Section 2 -->
<section class="pb-16 md:pt-28 md:pb-24 overflow-hidden relative">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5 parallax" data-speed="0.2">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-repeat" style="background-image: url('/dot-pattern.png');"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="container-custom relative">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="pl-10">
                <div class="pt-10">
                <h1 class="animate-on-scroll delay-0 text-blue text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold leading-tight">
                   Our Commitment to Health
                </h1>    
            </div>        
                <p class="animate-on-scroll delay-1 mt-6 text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-lg">
                   Bawa Medical Mart, is a name synonymous with trust and excellence in the medical industry. 
                   Established in 1961 by two visionary founders, K. A. Abdul Hai and K. A. 
                   Sheik Dawood, the company has proudly served the community for over six decades.
                   With 63 years of unparalleled experience, Bawa Medicals has built a strong reputation
                   for providing high-quality medical products and exceptional customer service. Our commitment 
                   to enhancing healthcare accessibility and reliability has made us a trusted name among healthcare 
                   professionals and individuals alike.
                </p> 
        </div>    
      
        <div class="animate-on-scroll delay-4">
        <div class="relative hover-zoom rounded-xl">
          <div class="absolute -inset-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple to-blue rounded-xl blur opacity-30 transition-opacity duration-300 hover:opacity-50"></div>
          <div class="relative bg-white rounded-xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
            <img 
              src="/showcase.jpg" 
              alt="Showcase banner" 
              class="w-full h-auto transition-all duration-500"
              width="700"
              height="500"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
           
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Section 3 -->
<section class="pb-16 md:pt-28 md:pb-24 overflow-hidden relative">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5 parallax" data-speed="0.2">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-repeat" style="background-image: url('/dot-pattern.png');"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="container-custom relative">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">

      <div class="animate-on-scroll delay-4">
        <div class="relative hover-zoom rounded-xl">
          <div class="absolute -inset-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple to-blue rounded-xl blur opacity-30 transition-opacity duration-300 hover:opacity-50"></div>
          <div class="relative bg-white rounded-xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
            <img 
              src="/advice-banner.jpg" 
              alt="Advice banner" 
              class="w-full h-auto transition-all duration-500"
              width="700"
              height="500"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        </div>

      <div class="pl-10">
                <div class="pt-10">
                <h1 class="animate-on-scroll delay-0 text-blue text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold leading-tight">
                  Our Core Values And Principle
                </h1>    
            </div>        
                <p class="animate-on-scroll delay-1 mt-6 text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-lg">
                   To provide reliable healthcare products with exceptional customer service, 
                   ensuring that every individual receives the care and attention they deserve.
                </p> 
        </div>    
           
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<PROFESSIONAL />
</Layout>